relevant_findings.heent: Pupils equal, round, reactive to light; extraocular movements intact. No scleral icterus or conjunctival injection. Mucous membranes moist. No oral ulcers.
relevant_findings.neck: Supple, no lymphadenopathy, no jugular venous pressure elevation.
relevant_findings.lungs: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, or rhonchi. Normal respiratory effort.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops.
relevant_findings.abdomen: Soft, with tenderness in the epigastric region, non-distended, normal bowel sounds, no hepatosplenomegaly.
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm and well perfused, no cyanosis, clubbing, or edema.
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert and oriented to person, place, and time; cranial nerves II-XII intact.
relevant_findings.psychiatric: Appropriate, tearful when discussing home situation, denies any suicidal ideation currently.
